0.9.8.name: wordpress/wp-zillow
0.9.8.description:
EASY TEMPLATE CUSTOMIZATION FOR BETTER DISPLAY OF CHARTS NOW ADDED THIS RELEASE

The UltimateIDX Presents, WP Zillow API for WordPress Real Estate Blogging at its best. Developed originally for our client use only, we have released this tool as a contribution to the WordPress community in support of the Worlds best Real Estate website platform, WordPress. This plugin provides blog website owners with a truly easy to manage easy to integrate charting solution for Zillow Demographics that can be put into your blogs posts and pages.

Tested with version 2.8.4 and WordPress MU, the plugin can support hundreds of chart examples and can be displayed or presented based entirely on area demographics or right down to the very address you are blogging about.
